						<h2>Pedobear Coupon</h2>
<p><a id="permlink-0" href="http://www.thesmokinggun.com/file/pedobear-coupon?page=0">http://www.thesmokinggun.com/file/pedobear-coupon?page=0</a></p>
						</div>
						<div class="doc_left">
							<img src="http://i.cdn.turner.com/dr/teg/tsg/release/sites/default/files/imagecache/750x970/documents/1pedobearoffender.jpg" alt="" title=""  class="imagecache imagecache-750x970 imagecache-default imagecache-750x970_default" width="613" height="970" />
